---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Design Expertise" description="Expert electronics design services including microprocessors, FPGAs, high-speed interfaces, power supplies and EMC compliance. From specification to prototype.">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="reveal text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-8">Design Expertise</h1>

      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy mb-4">
          ntronIQ will work with you to define the shape of your project.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy mb-4">
          We work with the best tools to deliver excellence and guide our customers through the development, ensuring successful delivery.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Our services include:</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-lg text-navy">
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Formal Specification</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Schematic design</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Simulations</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> MTBF predictions</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> FMEA analysis</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> PCB Layout</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> 3D Modelling</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Testing</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Prototype / Full production quantities</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Areas of expertise:</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-lg text-navy">
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Microprocessor circuitry</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> High-speed memory interfaces</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> FPGA integration</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> ASIC integration</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Microcontrollers</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> ADC / DACs</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Ethernet, I2C, RS232/485</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Switch Mode Power supplies</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> EMI filter design</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> RF Filter design</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> EMC Compliance</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Amplifier design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal mt-12">
        <img
          src="/images/PCB2.jpg"
          alt="PCB Design"
          class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
